About this item

  • 1.32" HD Screen & Custom DialWith our unprecedented 1.32" HD vivid screen and full touch functionality, you can view your data in stunning colours, lifelike clarity and an expanded field of view. You can choose from existing watch faces, or download new ones from the app, or take a photo to change your favourite face to suit your everyday mood and occasion.
  • Customised WatchThe Best Combination of Style and Functionality. High-quality metal frame with 1.32" HD color display and 2.5D curved glass provides you with a more vivid and wider view. With the app connected, there are 100+ different beautiful dials to choose from. Also you can go for something totally unique with your own favorite pictures, such as your family, pets, idols. Whenever you raise your hand, the smart watch screen lights up to show off your personal style.
  • Health Monitor & Women Health CareSmart watch for android phones with advanced sensors provide insights to help you better understand your health and make a reasonable adjustment on your lifestyle. Keep an eye on your health metrics (24-hour heart rate, blood oxygen and sleep), as well as record female menstrual periods, personalize menstrual management and pregnancy preparation reminders for women.
  • Activity Tracker & Multi Sports ModesEnjoy sports modes (walking, running, cycling, football...) with this fitness tracker. From indoor to outdoor activities, this activity tracker has it all. The fitness watch keeps an accurate record of your activities throughout the day and can track a variety of real-time data such as calories, distance, steps, etc. during your workout so you know your exercise status and make improvements accordingly, it is the perfect choice for fitness enthusiasts
  • Multifunctional Smart Watch & IP68 Waterproof Music controller, camera control, weather, automatic light up, breathing training, phone search, alarm clock, timer, stopwatch, etc. The smart watch with text and call is IP68 water resistant, whether you sweat or get splashed by a light drizzle, it can handle it all. The watch is compatible with iOS 11.0+ and Android 6.0+. Not suitable for PC or tablet.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
